                <h1>What to Expect After a Job Background Check</h1>
                <p>After a background check for a job, employers review your history, including criminal records, employment history, and education credentials. Depending on the results, they may proceed with the hiring process, request further clarification, or reevaluate your application. Transparency and honesty in your application are crucial during this stage.</p>
